      "Western Moral Thinkers (Part 2)",
      "Indian Moral Thinkers (Part 1)",
      "Indian Moral Thinkers (Part 2)",
      "Attitude",
      "Corruption in System",
      "Corruption in Politics",
      "Code of Conduct & Code of Ethics",
      "Corporate Governance",
      "Prominent Schools & Thinkers of Ethics",
      "Ethics in International Relations",
      "Ethical Ideas in Religions",
    ],
  },
  {
    subject: "Indian Society",
    icon: "users",
    summary: "Caste, secularism, communalism, urbanization, women.",
    lectures: [
      "Salient Features of Indian Society",
      "Caste System in India",
      "Issues & Challenges of Caste System",
      "Concept of Secularism",
      "Concept of Communalism",
      "Concept of Regionalism",
      "Backward Classes in India",
      "Scheduled Castes in India",
      "Scheduled Tribes In India",
      "Women & Related Issues in India",
      "Issues of Urbanization & Remedies",
