      "Fiscal Policy & Taxation (Part 2)",
      "Union Budget & Public Finance (Part 1)",
      "Union Budget & Public Finance (Part 2)",
      "Banking Sector & Financial Stability",
      "Inflation & Price Stability",
      "Money & Financial Markets",
      "External Sector & Global Trade",
      "Key Global Economic Institutions",
      "System of Planning In India",
      "Economic Reforms in India",
      "Emerging & Contemporary Economic Issues",
    ],
  },
  {
    subject: "Agriculture",
    icon: "sprout",
    summary: "Agriculture in economy, irrigation, land reforms.",
    lectures: [
      "Overview of Agriculture in Indian Economy",
